  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_52b9cfa244be85430102ac9810bb4373">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Photographs taken for Fiske by E. Thorbergsson [i.e Eiríkur Þorbergsson] in June of 1902 in Grímsey, Iceland, of people and places. Includes one photograph taken by Anna M. Magnúsdóttir of Guðný Guðmundsdóttir in July of 1901.</p>  </scopecontent>
